  "texts": [
    "Traditional learning tools and pedagogical strategies may have to be modified in order to satisfy the demands of students who constantly seek novel knowledge, learning methods, or ideas via interaction.",
    "In such a scenario, students will be able to adopt new technologies such as metaverse-based learning environments, and deal with a high degree of unpredictability in the real world.",
    "Additionally, given that learners with high PIIT tend to be more self-directed and have a strong desire for personalized learning, instructors should design metaverse-based learning experiences that allow learners to personalize their learning journey.",
    "This could include personalized learning paths, adaptive assessments, and individualized feedback.",
    "Instructors also are required to encourage risk-taking and failure."
  ],
